# #407 / §A51 — threat-feed publisher private keys MUST NEVER land in
# this repo per [[push-policy-public-repo]]. Both the canonical default
# location AND any *.pem files inside feeds/ are blocked. The PUBKEY
# (feeds/*.pubkey + *.pub) IS safe to commit.
*.ed25519.pem
publisher.ed25519.pem
feeds/*.pem
feeds/*.private*

